---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Icon from '../components/Icon.astro';
const title = "Stopping ransomware before it reached clinical systems - Case Study - SubZeroSec";
const description = "A combined assessment found that a single compromised workstation could reach clinical systems across a flat network, and mapped the segmentation needed to stop it.";
---
<Base title={title} description={description} active="case-studies">
<section class="phead">
  <div class="phbg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <i>/</i> <a href="case-studies.html">Case Studies</a> <i>/</i> <span>National Healthcare Network</span></div><span class="eyebrow">Healthcare</span>
    <h1>Stopping ransomware before it reached clinical systems</h1>
    <p class="lead">A combined assessment found that a single compromised workstation could reach clinical systems across a flat network, and mapped the segmentation needed to stop it.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="sec light cutA"><div class="geo" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="wrap"><div class="metrics"><div class="metric"><div class="m">0</div><div class="l">critical findings at re-test</div></div><div class="metric"><div class="m">3 wks</div><div class="l">to full remediation of high-risk paths</div></div><div class="metric"><div class="m">100%</div><div class="l">of clinical networks segmented from corporate IT</div></div></div><div class="detail" style="margin-top:2.4rem"><div class="dprose"><h3 class="colh">The challenge</h3><p>After ransomware crippled a peer organization, the network needed to know whether the same attack could spread to systems that directly support patient care. Years of acquisitions had left the internal network largely flat and poorly understood.</p><h3 class="colh">Our approach</h3><ul class="checks"><li><span class="ck"><Icon name="check" /></span> Performed an assumed-breach assessment starting from a single standard workstation</li><li><span class="ck"><Icon name="check" /></span> Mapped lateral movement paths from corporate IT toward clinical and device networks</li><li><span class="ck"><Icon name="check" /></span> Tested the resilience of backup and recovery systems to a ransomware-style attack</li><li><span class="ck"><Icon name="check" /></span> Delivered a prioritized segmentation plan tied to the specific paths we exploited</li></ul></div><aside class="dside"><div class="aside-card"><h4>Sector</h4><p class="asp">Healthcare</p></div><div class="aside-card"><h4>Services used</h4><div class="relinks"><a href="service-vapt.html">Penetration Testing (VAPT) <Icon name="arrow-right" /></a><a href="service-threat-hunting.html">Threat Hunting <Icon name="arrow-right" /></a></div></div><a class="btn btn-fill asidebtn" href="contact.html">Start a conversation <Icon name="arrow-right" /></a></aside></div></div></section>
<section class="sec dark"><div class="wrap"><div class="bigquote"><p>&ldquo;We thought we understood our network. The assessment showed us we didn't, and gave us a plan we could actually execute.&rdquo;</p><div class="by">&mdash; Chief Information Security Officer, National Healthcare Network</div></div></div></section>
<section class="sec light cutC"><div class="geo" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="wrap"><div class="cta-in"><span class="eyebrow">Get ahead of zero</span><h2>Ready to see yourself the way an <span class="r">adversary would?</span></h2><p>Book a scoped assessment - we will map what is reachable, prove what is exploitable, and give you a ranked path to closing it before someone finds it first.</p><a href="contact.html" class="btn btn-fill">Book a free scoping call <Icon name="arrow-right" /></a></div></div></section>
</Base>
